OL,3,CReform pledges mandatory 'whole life'
OL,4,Csentences for child rapists
OL,6,FReform UK would introduce mandatory
OL,7,F"whole life" orders for child rapists,
OL,8,Fthe party's head of policy has said.
OL,10,FOffenders convicted of the crime would
OL,11,Fnever become eligible for parole,
OL,12,Faccording to the plans announced by
OL,13,FZia Yusuf.
OL,15,FThe policy has been "factored in" to
OL,16,FReform's plans to free up prison
OL,17,Fcapacity by deporting foreign
OL,18,Fcriminals to their country of origin
OL,19,Fand building "Nightingale prisons",
OL,20,Fthe party sad.
