OL,3,CReform pledges mandatory 'whole life'
OL,4,Csentences for child rapists
OL,6,FLife sentences can be given to child
OL,7,Frapists at a judge's discretion under
OL,8,Fexisting rules, with an offence range
OL,9,Fof six to 19 years for offences
OL,10,Fagainst children under 13.
OL,12,FWhole life orders differ from standard
OL,13,Flife sentences, whereby a minimum term
OL,14,Fis served before potential parole.
OL,16,FThey are given in cases where the
OL,17,Fcrime was deemed so serious that the
OL,18,Foffender should never be released from
OL,19,Fprison.
