OL,6,F"A Reform government will introduce
OL,7,Fmandatory minimum life sentences for
OL,8,Fthose who rape children. It is
OL,9,Fshameful that this is not already the
OL,10,Flaw.
OL,12,F"It is a stain on our national
OL,13,Fconscience that grooming gangs were
OL,14,Fallowed to operate for years with
OL,15,Fimpunity, and in many cases still do.
OL,17,F"Under Conservative governments, the
OL,18,Faverage sentence for the rape of a
OL,19,Fchild under 13 fell to as little as
OL,20,Fnine years.
